text: Налице е кворум – откривам пленарното заседание.
translation-bg: I shall open the plenary session.
translation-sla: There's a quorum. I'm opening the plenary.
translation-zls: There's a quorum - I'm opening the plenary session.

text: Уважаеми народни представители, постъпи искане от Президентската администрация за извънреден брой на „Държавен вестник“ в утрешния ден, в който ще бъде обнародван указът за разпускане на 43-ото народно събрание и насрочване на предсрочните парламентарни избори.
translation-bg: Honourable Members of Parliament, there was a request from the President's Administration for an extraordinary number of the Official Journal on the day of tomorrow, which will be published the decree for the dissolution of the 43rd National Assembly and the timing of the early parliamentary elections.
translation-sla: Dear People's Representatives, a request was made by the Presidential Administration for an extraordinary number of the State Gazette on tomorrow, on which an order for the 43rd People's Assembly to be dissolved and for the early parliamentary elections to be scheduled.
translation-zls: Dear People's Representatives, a request has been made by the Presidential Administration for an extraordinary number of State Journals on the morning of which the order to disband the 43rd National Assembly will be reproduced and the early parliamentary elections will be scheduled.

text: По тази причина Проектът на програма за работата на Народното събрание е за времето от 25 до 26 януари 2017 г., тъй като последното пленарно заседание за тази легислатура на парламента ще бъде в четвъртък, 26 януари.
translation-bg: For this reason, the draft programme for the work of the National Assembly is for the period from 25 to 26 January 2017, as the last plenary session for this parliamentary legislation will be on Thursday, 26 January.
translation-sla: For this reason, the draft programme for the work of the National Assembly is for the period from 25 to 26 January 2017, as the last plenary meeting for this parliamentary legislation will be held on Thursday, 26 January.
translation-zls: For this reason, the draft programme for the work of the National Assembly is for the period from 25 to 26 January 2017, as the last plenary session for this House legislation will be held on Thursday, 26 January.

text: Ще дойде времето и за господин Ерменков, но преди това – постъпило е предложение от Димитър Делчев и група народни представители за включване в Програмата за тази седмица на първо четене на Законопроекта за старите столици на България с вх. № 654 01-139, внесен на 9 декември 2016 г.
translation-bg: The time will come for Mr. Ermenkov, but before that... is a proposal from Dimitar Delchev and a group of MPs for inclusion in the Program for this week at the first reading of the Bill for the Old Capitals of Bulgaria with. No 654 01-139, submitted on 9 December 2016.
translation-sla: The time will come for Mr. Ermenkov, but before that – a proposal has been made by Dimitar Delchev and a group of national representatives for inclusion in the Programme for this week on the first reading of the Bill for the Old Capitals of Bulgaria. No 654 01-139, entered on 9 December 2016.
translation-zls: The time will come for Mr. Ermenkov, but before that – a proposal has been made by Dimitar Delchev and a group of folk representatives for inclusion in the Programme for this week at the first reading of the Law on the old capitals of Bulgaria with whh. No 654 01-139, tabled on 9 December 2016.

text: Предложението е недопустимо, тъй като не са изтекли сроковете по нашия Правилник.
translation-bg: The proposal is inadmissible because the time limits under our Rules have not expired.
translation-sla: The proposal is inadmissible as the deadlines for our Rules of Procedure have not expired.
translation-zls: The proposal is inadmissible as the deadlines under our Rules have not expired.

text: Срокът е двумесечен за обсъждане на законопроектите на първо гласуване.
translation-bg: The deadline is two months to discuss the bills of first vote.
translation-sla: The deadline is two months to discuss bills in the first vote.
translation-zls: The deadline is two months for discussion of first-vote bills.
